    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331040/extras/cc99fefb3cc8c35244c933df87ea3691.avif?t=1743233970\" width=590 height=184 /></span>「片桐同学想依靠我 」是由日本知名游戏社团キリンジェット制作，Hanabi games汉化发行的一款RPG游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「片桐同学想依靠我 」是「片桐同学非常冷淡 」的续作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331040/extras/e0b7a7745f272c865b9f7081a515256b.avif?t=1743233970\" width=550 height=70 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你在一间昏暗的房间里醒来，面前是你熟悉的片桐同学。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你为什么会在这里？是谁干的？她为什么会在这里......？等等...... 你以前来过这里吧 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一切看起来都一样，但似乎有些不对劲...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个简短的密室逃脱 RPG 游戏中，你要找出是什么原因让你回到这里！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331040/extras/1a9099419e13bf2944369596ba2981e9.avif?t=1743233970\" width=550 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331040/extras/8ed17b1f70a02a523407c55eb7990f91.avif?t=1743233970\" width=550 height=380 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331040/extras/da24b66e25ea69f94ad922421bd258fc.avif?t=1743233970\" width=550 height=70 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jrpg </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解谜逃脱 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >迷人的故事剧情</p></li></ul>",
